Project Overview
Student will develop a Student Management System using Java and object oriented programming principles.
The system should :-
- Allow student registration(Name, ID, course, Grade).
- Implement encapsulating using private field and public getters and setters.
- Store student record using and arraylist or a database (for advanced students. )
- Use exceptional handling for invalid inputs
- Implement file handling to save student records
- Use multi threading to simulate multiple user accessing the system

	Bonus feature
- Implement an interactive console based menu
- Use GUI(JavaFX or Swing) for advanced versions
